# AST internals

AST construction is the semantic centre of the frontend. It consumes sorted headers, resolves declarations, checks executable bodies, folds constants and templates, and prepares the clean input that HIR generation needs.

## Category contract

- `build_ast_environment` resolves declarations and builds shared semantic state.
- `emit_ast_nodes` parses executable bodies against the completed environment.
- `finalize_ast` cleans up and produces HIR-ready structures.

