## Category-wide invariants

- Type identity is `TypeId` in the active `TypeEnvironment`: `DataType` is parse-only or diagnostic-only after resolution.
- Contextual coercion resolves at explicit frontend boundaries before HIR.
- Generics, traits and cast evidence resolve before HIR.
- Template semantics finish before HIR lowers runtime templates.
- Const page fragments stay outside HIR.
